{"tid":1332988,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙特回應聯署支持中國新疆政策：「全世界冇地方比沙特更關切穆斯林狀況。我們支持中國發展政策，政策幫助人民脫離貧困。」","createTime":"2019-07-19T13:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T15:16:13.000Z","uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e7e9f6601f2b74574aedf9231bbdb4ffbe5e7d","tid":1332988,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3937599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3937599&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=2d9dd8c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3937599</a><br />\n<br />\n22國上週致函聯合國人權理事會（UNHRC），籲中國停止大規模拘留。沙烏地、俄羅斯及另外35國則以聯名信作為回應，讚揚這是「中國在人權領域取得顯著成就」。<br />\n<br />\n詢及沙烏地為何加入聯名，沙烏地駐聯合國大使穆亞里米（Abdallah Al-Mouallimi）在紐約告訴記者：「這封信講述中國的發展工作，只講這個，沒提別的。」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「全世界沒有其他地方比沙烏地阿拉伯更關切穆斯林的狀況。我們在信中說的是，我們支持中國的發展政策，這些政策幫助人民脫離貧困。」<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社取得的聯名信副本，信中寫說新疆重拾安全，並說所有族群的基本人權都獲得保障。聯名信寫道：「面對恐怖主義與極端主義的重大挑戰，中國在新疆採取了一系列反恐及去激進化措施，包括設立職業教育及訓練中心。」<br />\n<br />\n人權觀察（Human Rights Watch）駐聯合國主任夏邦諾（Louis Charbonneau）表示，穆亞里米對這封信的描述，猶如「一巴掌打在受中國迫害的穆斯林臉上，不正確到荒謬的地步」。<br />\n<br />\n美國和德國本月稍早在聯合國安全理事會的閉門會議上抨擊中國設立拘留營，中國則回應外交官說，他們沒有權利在安理會提及此事，因為這是中國內務。"},{"pid":"562a6abdd9e0043993894707196a0be4b8c8c291","tid":1332988,"uid":146583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">除咗升級裝備 諗唔到有咩可以做？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入嚟睇吓運動嘅出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n點評時下局勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4882eaee230d95da77d092ad24f8407cc43850d8","tid":1332988,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a067f237b194a83deb4384298037639d3486f29","tid":1332988,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:54:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c094a374af79d5699d2c8d1081acab2fc5185d20","tid":1332988,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"支持你就唔出聲<br />\n反對你就強烈譴責人地干預<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0596521541072b144613be885e3946d7d9724b54","tid":1332988,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T15:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}